#. <section class="sutta" id="sn8.11"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn8.11:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn8.11:0.2"
msgid "1. Vaṅgīsavagga"
msgstr "1. With Vaṅgīsa"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn8.11:0.3"
msgid "11. Gaggarāsutta"
msgstr "11. At Gaggarā"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.421"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.11:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā campāyaṃ viharati gaggarāya pokkharaṇiyā tīre mahatā "
"bhikkhusaṃghena saddhiṃ pañcamattehi bhikkhusatehi sattahi ca upāsakasatehi "
"sattahi ca upāsikāsatehi anekehi ca devatāsahassehi."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Campā on the banks of the Gaggarā "
"Lotus Pond, together with a large Saṅgha of around five hundred mendicants, "
"seven hundred male and seven hundred female lay followers, and many "
"thousands of deities."

#. VAR: atirocati → ativirocati (mr)
msgctxt "sn8.11:1.2"
msgid "Tyāssudaṃ bhagavā atirocati vaṇṇena ceva yasasā ca."
msgstr "But the Buddha outshone them all in beauty and glory."

msgctxt "sn8.11:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato vaṅgīsassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Venerable Vaṅgīsa thought:"

msgctxt "sn8.11:1.4"
msgid ""
"“ayaṃ kho bhagavā campāyaṃ viharati gaggarāya pokkharaṇiyā tīre mahatā "
"bhikkhusaṃghena saddhiṃ pañcamattehi bhikkhusatehi sattahi ca upāsakasatehi "
"sattahi ca upāsikāsatehi anekehi ca devatāsahassehi."
msgstr ""
"“The Buddha is staying near Campā on the banks of the Gaggarā Lotus Pond, "
"together with a large Saṅgha of around five hundred mendicants, seven "
"hundred male and seven hundred female lay followers, and many thousands of "
"deities."

msgctxt "sn8.11:1.5"
msgid "Tyāssudaṃ bhagavā atirocati vaṇṇena ceva yasasā ca."
msgstr "And he outshines them all in beauty and glory."

msgctxt "sn8.11:1.6"
msgid "Yannūnāhaṃ bhagavantaṃ sammukhā sāruppāya gāthāya abhitthaveyyan”ti."
msgstr "Why don’t I extoll him in his presence with appropriate verses?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.11:2.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā vaṅgīso uṭṭhāyāsanā ekaṃsaṃ uttarāsaṅgaṃ karitvā yena "
"bhagavā tenañjaliṃ paṇāmetvā bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Vaṅgīsa got up from his seat, arranged his robe over one "
"shoulder, raised his joined palms toward the Buddha, and said:"

msgctxt "sn8.11:2.2"
msgid "“paṭibhāti maṃ, bhagavā, paṭibhāti maṃ, sugatā”ti."
msgstr ""
"“I feel inspired to speak, Blessed One! I feel inspired to speak, Holy One!”"

msgctxt "sn8.11:2.3"
msgid "“Paṭibhātu taṃ, vaṅgīsā”ti bhagavā avoca."
msgstr "“Then speak as you feel inspired,” said the Buddha."

msgctxt "sn8.11:2.4"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā vaṅgīso bhagavantaṃ sammukhā sāruppāya gāthāya abhitthavi:"
msgstr ""
"Then Vaṅgīsa extolled the Buddha in his presence with appropriate verses:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.196"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.11:3.1"
msgid "“Cando yathā vigatavalāhake nabhe,"
msgstr "“Like the moon on a cloudless night,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.11:3.2"
msgid "Virocati vigatamalova bhāṇumā;"
msgstr "like the shining stainless sun,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.11:3.3"
msgid "Evampi aṅgīrasa tvaṃ mahāmuni,"
msgstr "so too Aṅgīrasa, O great sage,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.11:3.4"
msgid "Atirocasi yasasā sabbalokan”ti."
msgstr "your glory outshines the entire world.”"
